I"¶<p>Delete this centos.repo (or change enabled=0 for all) and Create a new repository centos1.repo in /etc/yum.repos.d/ with the content:</p>

<p>[centos]
name=CentOS-7
baseurl=http://ftp.heanet.ie/pub/centos/7/os/x86_64/
enabled=1
gpgcheck=1
gpgkey=http://ftp.heanet.ie/pub/centos/7/os/x86_64/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-7</p>

<p>Then run</p>

<p>yum repolist</p>

<p>Now check if you can install any package like</p>

<p>yum install nmap -y</p>
